{"tid":589939,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★為應對創新科技：35% 公司計劃增聘請\"新員工\"！！","createTime":"2018-03-12T07:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T11:43:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c31561ae8613d60f97ae2bf0b636a353b58595","tid":589939,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:59:38.000Z","msg":"數碼轉型已不知不覺間在各企業之中開始進行部署並實踐！然而隨著市場衝擊因素不斷浮現，香港金融服務行業將於 2018 年面對重大轉變。由招聘公司 Robert Half 委託進行的一項最新獨立研究發現，為了應對 2018 年各項重大改革，44% 金融服務行業的 CFO 計劃提升現有員工技能以應付轉變，<span style=\"color: red;\">35% 則計劃聘請新員工</span>。<br />\n<br />\n絶大部份香港金融服務行業領袖均相信員工能應付這些顛覆大勢的力量並取得佳績。在技術能力方面，有 92% 受訪者認為公司剛畢業的員工具備充足的科技技能、89% 受訪者就相信公司一般僱員，還有 99% 相信公司管理層成員達到要求。在軟技能方面，<span style=\"color: red;\">95% 受訪者相信剛畢業的員工具備這些技能</span>、<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkitblog.com/?p=41966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkitblog.com%2F%3Fp%3D41966&d=JpxaRj1s82kYk0V6mTQ666NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=7ffc402a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkitblog.com/?p=41966</a>"},{"pid":"12a537e63a5996800b12eedd4a9e0ff747824d5a","tid":589939,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T07:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ac27d1ac7b87331032fbb174ebfedcd6d4b287","tid":589939,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T08:00:12.000Z","msg":"95% 受訪者相信剛畢業的員工具備這些技能<br />\n95% 受訪者相信剛畢業的員工具備這些技能<br />\n95% 受訪者相信剛畢業的員工具備這些技能<br />\n95% 受訪者相信剛畢業的員工具備這些技能<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgm